cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "CorSeaCare_yolo: detecting, counting and characterising marine plastic particles in sieve photos"
abstract: >-
  An open, local (Apple-Silicon) computer-vision tool to detect, count, classify and
  measure marine plastic particles in photographs of Manta-net sieve samples, built around
  a human-in-the-loop annotation workflow for the CorSeaCare citizen-science expedition.
type: software
authors:
